implement F.3 tunnel_wrap:
  generate tunnel constants from the declared row 09 topology.
  intercept left movement at the left tunnel endpoint.
  intercept right movement at the right tunnel endpoint.
  teleport to the paired endpoint, then set the next target cell in the same direction.
  preserve score-on-consume behavior.

implement F.4 pacman_expiration:
  add an expiration state flag and countdown timer.
  when expiration begins, stop movement and ignore input.
  use the tunnel as the temporary expiration trigger.
  after timeout, reset Pac-Man to start cell and clear requested direction.
  preserve score and consumed item map.

implement F.5 multiple_lives:
  add lives state after expiration works.
  initialize lives to 3.
  decrement lives on expiration.
  reset Pac-Man if lives remain.
  enter game-over if lives reach 0.
